Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:45.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The grand prize is a hot \Nsprings vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:47.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.36,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hot springs would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll land the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:53.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.16,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your consolation prize. Pocket tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:04.99,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your tissues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:07.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Last one! This time I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:09.13,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:09.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.75,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:14.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:17.52,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Third prize! You'll be set for\N the cold winter with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:20.06,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,You've won a warm kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.39,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:23.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.07,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going anywhere, Yamashita-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.49,sign_4316_49_Deadline,Calendaer,0000,0000,0000,,Deadline
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.48,Main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Home to my family in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.77,Main,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you some nama \Nchocolates as souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.50,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Nama chocolates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.92,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kobayashi-san? \NGoing home to your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.86,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,I have Winter Comiket at the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:17.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Aah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.48,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,The train's leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:25.72,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.06,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.30,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.34,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of stuff happened this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:37.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:40.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:41.56,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This year's work is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.80,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, do you have \Nto go to work anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I'm off until the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.70,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:59.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so busy, so please take \Nit easy over the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:06.42,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is heaven. I'm glad we won the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I need to start preparing \Nthe New Year's dishes soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I even borrowed the tools to \Npound mochi and soba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go that all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a maid's responsibility \Nto take charge and make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,the seasonal events are carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you need to use the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:34.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, you're a maid. Go for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.61,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, guess I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:42.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Kobayashi, could you hit \Nthe switch on the rice cooker?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.92,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Pass the remote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.08,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.34,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.85,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,This is New Year's curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.86,sign_7106_89_Delicious__Tomat,Boxes,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious\N{\c&H4B1EB9&\b1}Tomato\N{\c&H2A7240&}Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.86,sign_7106_87_Honey_Curry_Mild,Boxes,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAF70F1&}Mild\N{\c&H0F65EE&}Honey\N{\c&H865EDF&}Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.86,sign_7106_88_Sun_Curry_Mild,Boxes,0000,0000,0000,,Sun Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.86,sign_7106_89_Mild,Boxes,0000,0000,0000,,Mild
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.09,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Is it—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.40,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,It's mild.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.40,sign_7229_92_Sun_Curry,Boxes,0000,0000,0000,,Sun Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.40,sign_7229_93_Mild,Boxes,0000,0000,0000,,Mild
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.33,sign_7411_95_December_29th,,0000,0000,0000,,- December 29th -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.59,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New Year's parlor trick tournament \Nwill be on January 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.09,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can look forward to several outstanding \Nguests performing in our competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:31.77,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our huge New Year's bargain sale starts soon!\N Doors open at 6:30AM on the 1st!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.89,sign_7411_95_December_29th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,271)}- December 30th -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:46.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So I can just pound the New Year's \Nsoba tomorrow before we eat it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:49.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, isn't this a lot of work for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:53.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, these are my natural duties as a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:58.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, but I feel like we're \Nforgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:07.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.78,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:15.35,Main,Sasakibe,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru-chan, good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, they're calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Sasakibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.77,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.64,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I made too much candied \Nsweet potatoes with chestnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.15,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Have some if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.25,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we didn't make any of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hold on one moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some mochi we pounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it in your freezer \Nyou can keep it from molding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.29,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.01,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.96,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Yana. Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:03.81,Main,Yan,0000,0000,0000,,I got a lot of mandarin oranges from my home. \NHave some. They're sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.43,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This many? Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.14,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:10.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please take some of our mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.23,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:19.78,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Going by the pattern thus far,\N as soon as I climb under again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:30.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Sone. Is this a rooster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:33.15,Main,Soune,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, next year's animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This rooster is well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it on display right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some of the mochi we made. Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyom, nyom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyom, nyom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good job again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:52.07,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we received this from Mr. Sone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.07,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Rooster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.57,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the zodiac animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.77,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's a zodiac animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There are twelve animals \Nin the Chinese zodiac.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.66,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(773,1)}Zodiac Animals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Rat, Ox, Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:07:59.66,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Rat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.41,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ox
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:03.00,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit, Dragon, Snake, Horse, Ram,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:03.50,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.00,sign_11593_158_Dragon,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:04.50,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Snake
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.13,sign_11593_158_Dragon,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Horse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:05.88,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Ram
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.50,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey, Rooster, Dog, and Pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.25,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Rooster
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.00,sign_11416_150_Zodiac_Animals,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Dog
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:08.84,sign_11593_158_Dragon,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Pig
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:10.19,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:15.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It came up when I was searching the \Nnet for all things New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:23.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they say the order of the \Nanimals was decided by who
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:27.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,reached God fastest on the \Nmorning of the new year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:30.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, there is that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:34.19,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The Rat stole first place by \Nhopping a ride on the Ox.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.20,sign_12254_175_God,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(775,1)}God
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:34.95,sign_12333_177_Seriously__,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,"Seriously!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:39.99,sign_12254_175_God,,0000,0000,0000,,God
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.42,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you can't you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:44.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for a dragon to come after \Nan Ox or Tiger, let alone a Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.23,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this mandarin orange is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:58.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:03.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,For getting along with the neighbors,\N and everything else you've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.81,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was forgetting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.92,sign_13509_196__postcard,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Greetings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.14,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't written one of these in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.27,sign_14027_200__shop_sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy Grab
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.77,sign_7411_95_December_29th,,0000,0000,0000,,- December 31st -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.37,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do you feel about your \Nfirst performance on the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.18,Main-Top,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I wrote my lyrics down on \Nmy hand so I wouldn't forget them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:57.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I had the noodle shop owner in the \Nshopping district teach me the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:59.72,Main-Top,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my palms are so sweaty \Nthey've all disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.03,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Put my kimono on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she promised to join \NMiss Saikawa on her first shrine visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:11.05,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She lent me a kimono so we \Ncan wear them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A kimono, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.55,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:20.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:24.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible, Miss Kobayashi. \NThat's like a magic trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago my mother \Ntaught me the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nice. It looks cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You want to wear one, too, then, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:32.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.24,sign_15231_221_First_Shrine_Vis,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,First Shrine Visit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:45.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad my kimono fits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:47.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,With a kimono, you can adjust \Nthe size for the chest, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:48.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,These past few days we've been losing \Nto the temptation of the kotatsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.42,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,but going outside for a change is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.53,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.62,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:02.84,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Saikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.30,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.03,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.66,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:14.59,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Should I not be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.29,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into Elma over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:20.85,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you could eat lots \Nof unusual food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Lucoa-san, what's with your kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.23,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:28.86,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.56,Main-Top,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's your idea of traditional?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.00,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kobayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:40.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that looks good on you, Mr. Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.39,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.13,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.98,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry! Before the amazake's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.24,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.03,sign_17218_253_Episode_11,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.03,sign_17218_254_Year_End__New_Ye,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Year End, New Year! (No Comiket Bit This Time)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.03,sign_17348_255_Fried_Chicken,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fried Chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.03,sign_17384_255_Amazake_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Amazake\N{\fs12}It's delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.03,sign_17384_257_1_Cup_100_yen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,1 Cup {\c&H0C9EF9&}100 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.93,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,So sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.31,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nostalgic flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:20.63,sign_17485_256_Delicious_Amazak,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious Amazake
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.66,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.83,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I used to drink \Nsomething like this often.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.58,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,It takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:20.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and because you got \Ndrunk you and your sister—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.30,sign_17758_264_Evil_Banishing_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Evil-Banishing\NArrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.48,0:12:26.20,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.30,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.17,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanna-san. Want to buy matching ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.42,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Matching?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:32.02,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.76,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of this r-relationship charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.77,sign_18031_274_Relationships,Charm,0000,0000,0000,,Relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A charm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.36,sign_18282_277_Academics,Charm,0000,0000,0000,,Academics
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.36,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,An academics charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:48.72,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,One I made would work way better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:51.11,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need any charms, Shouta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.82,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from a family of mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.27,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll achieve my desires myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.69,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.41,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You bought an evil-banishing arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.67,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,It might be useful for \Nresearching new curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,How'd Comiket go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.77,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, we sold out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're as popular as ever, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:16.22,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Faf-kun's "Curse Anthology 2"\N didn't sell any though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,He produced a second after the \Nfirst didn't sell this summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.01,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.23,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.36,sign_19259_294_Fortune_Telling,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune Telling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.49,sign_19286_295_Dummy_text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune Telling\N{\fs18}Number Twelve\N{\fs20}Great Blessing\N\NLuck
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Georgie, you got great blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:32.80,Main,Georgie,0000,0000,0000,,It's a blessing too great for a maid. \NYou should have it, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:37.02,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. It's your luck, Sis—... Georgie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:40.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, look! My fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.46,sign_19286_295_Dummy_text,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune Telling\N{\fs18}Number Twelve\N{\fs20}Great Curse\N\NLuck
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.77,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Great curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:45.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your wishes will prove difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:52.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The one you wait for will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.96,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That which you've lost, won't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get, but it\Nsounds like a great curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:02.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess it also means things'll \Nonly get better from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.53,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't it almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.86,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.61,Main,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:14.12,sign_20401_314_Saturday__Decemb,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday, December 31st
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:14.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this year's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:17.61,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Time sure flew by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.62,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen, twelve,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.63,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,eleven, ten, nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:25.62,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.63,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.63,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,six,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.64,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,five,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:31.59,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,four, three, two,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.87,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:34.95,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:36.59,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.04,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:40.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.35,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.39,0:14:46.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.53,sign_21280_331_Be_happy__,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.53,sign_21280_332_May_Dad_s_hips_g,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,May Dad's lower back\Nget a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.53,sign_21280_333_May_I_become__gr,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,May I become \Ngreat at soccer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.53,sign_21280_334_Land_a_job_,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Land a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.53,sign_21280_335_Cherish__our_fam,Signs,0000,0000,0000,,Cherish \Nour family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:53.09,Main,Georgie,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:54.71,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.60,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi, can I invite Saikawa over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.50,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's warm under the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take this chance \Nto invite everyone over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:06.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of food, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:10.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. We should let Saikawa-san's \Nand Shouta-kun's families know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, everyone, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the ozouni soup, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.98,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Did you make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to eat it \Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru and Kanna made the mochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.61,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,You went all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.30,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you made it, \NI'll eat it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.48,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.83,sign_22462_352_Disappointment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Slurp
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.68,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:44.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I learned the seasoning from \NMiss Kobayashi's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.14,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mild, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some sweet red bean soup later, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:51.74,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What meat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You get a special treat, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:59.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you countless times \Nnot to put in your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But it's about time you tried it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new year after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It still won't happen next \Nyear or the year after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.36,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Just climb in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The kotatsu's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:17.97,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsus are nice. Maybe we'll buy one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.09,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.43,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:54.27,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see the first sunrise of the year \Nwith Kanna-san, so this should be a good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.53,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:58.79,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,The first sunrise of the year is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.55,sign_24716_376_January_2nd,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(940,1)}- January 2nd -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:15.50,Main-Top,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, every year on January 2nd, \Nit's the annual Tokyo Bay Ekiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.66,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:19.67,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which team will win today's race to Nagaura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's on break until the new year's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.26,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't step away right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's closer to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Aah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:55.72,sign_24716_376_January_2nd,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(941,1)}- January 3rd -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.70,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, today's Tokyo Bay \NEkiden, on January 3rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.68,Main-Top,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The contenders for the win have \Nbeen narrowed down to two teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:59.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are these people running the \Nsame race as yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, today they're running back from Nagaura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.88,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Want to play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:06.48,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:08.23,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.93,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,First writing of the year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.52,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Anything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,...ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,...tsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.45,sign_26452_403_Kotatsu,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:25.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Looks fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.15,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.38,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.63,sign_26750_408_Mom,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What should I write?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.24,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.75,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:53.47,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.56,Italics,KM,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.36,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:18:59.79,Italics,KM,0000,0000,0000,,I got your New Year's card today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:02.61,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess it didn't make \Nit for the 1st, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:05.26,Italics,KM,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time you've ever sent a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Everyone doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:08.87,Italics,KM,0000,0000,0000,,We're well, we're well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It went out of bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.19,Main-Top,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.37,Italics,KM,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.53,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:17.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I have some friends over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.34,Italics,KM,0000,0000,0000,,So you're having fun, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.77,Main-Top,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.88,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:25.86,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Give everyone my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.58,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.40,sign_28137_436_Kobayashi_san,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who was on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:41.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,My mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:42.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.16,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She said all my folks are doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's ending soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:09.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi, you weren't going to \Nsee your family even for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:15.47,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, I spend New Year's \Nsleeping off the year's fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm on bad \Nterms with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Occasionally we chat on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is with human families?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:27.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's different for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:34.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, living over here's \Nthe life I've grown used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.49,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:40.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You could go back if you wanted to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to go see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:52.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Living here with you is my \Nlife now, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.34,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
